OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy this morning with some
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain. Gradually
OL,7,Fbrightening up this afternoon but
OL,8,Fthere will still be some showery rain
OL,9,Faround, this mainly in the east.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fsome late sunshine. Showers or some
OL,13,Flonger spells of rain will spread from
OL,14,Fthe southwest in the early hours.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSaturday:FAny overnight showers dying
OL,17,Fout in the morning. Otherwise a dry
OL,18,Fday with some sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
